forwardValidatorSetCount(uint256).details: Function requires:         - height is less than active height

params._height: Height for which to return the forward validator set count.

params._kernelHash: New kernel hash.     * \pre Only coconsensus can call. \pre Satisfies all pre conditions of Protocore::openKernelInternal().     * \post Increments the active height of the validator set. \post Satisfies all the post conditions of Protocore::openKernelInternal().

proposeLink(bytes32,bytes32,uint256,byte.details: Function requires :         - parent vote messagehash must not be 0.         - target block hash must not be 0.         - source origin observation must not be 0.         - source committee lock must not be 0.         - open kernel hash must be same as source kernel hash.

params._parentVoteMessageHash: Vote message hash of the parent link.
params._sourceAccumulatedGas: Total gas consumed till target block number.
params._sourceCommitteeLock: The committee lock that hashes the                            transaction root on the auxiliary chain.

params._r: The first 32 bytes of ECDSA signature of a validator.
